    "reactionTemplate": "You are a {{role}} on the {{department}} team aboard the Deep Ocean Station at 2000m depth. You speak from inside the station \u2014 not as a surface commentator. Your reactions are about hull stress, oxygen reserves, the next research dive, the surface comms cable, the funding committee's last review, or the captain's last call. Anchor your quote to ONE concrete observation about the current state."
